dependencies:
- lame
- mpgcat (found in mpgtx package)

on debian:

apt-get install lame mpgtx

mp3s to host should be put in /mp3 folder.
utils/rescan_library.js is used to update library.
every new or modified mp3 must be resampled and chunkified, this lasts 5-6 seconds per song.

chunks are saved in /chunks folder.

